This software is designed to be the perfect assistant for the game master in a role playing game

**********************
*    REQUIREMENTS    *
**********************

To compile, you need:
- g++
- C++ standard library STL (with development files)
- Qt4 (with development files)

**********************
*    INSTRUCTIONS    *
**********************

To compile GM-Assistant, execute the following commands:

./configure
make

Then, to launch GM-Assistant, just type:

./GM-Assistant
